*About* 
------------

       Police officer Virat Chavan ne diya vaada apne marte hue junior ko ke rakhenge woh khayal unki beti, Sai ka. Virat aur Sai bandh gaye anchaahe shaadi ke bandhan mai. snippet.title: Joker: Folie √Ä Deux | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
When you‚Äôre smiling, the whole world smiles with you. Joker: Folie √Ä Deux ‚Äì only in theaters and IMAX, October 4. #JokerMovie #FilmedForIMAX 

From acclaimed writer/director/producer Todd Phillips comes ‚ÄúJoker: Folie √Ä Deux,‚Äù the much-anticipated follow-up to 2019‚Äôs Academy Award-winning ‚ÄúJoker,‚Äù which earned more than $1 billion at the global box office and remains the highest-grossing R-rated film of all time.  The new film stars Joaquin Phoenix once again in his Oscar-winning dual role as Arthur Fleck/Joker, opposite Oscar winner Lady Gaga (‚ÄúA Star Is Born‚Äù).

‚ÄúJoker: Folie √Ä Deux‚Äù finds Arthur Fleck institutionalized at Arkham awaiting trial for his crimes as Joker. While struggling with his dual identity, Arthur not only stumbles upon true love, but also finds the music that's always been inside him.

The film also stars Oscar nominees Brendan Gleeson (‚ÄúThe Banshees of Inisherin‚Äù) and Catherine Keener (‚ÄúGet Out,‚Äù ‚ÄúCapote‚Äù), alongside Zazie Beetz, reprising her role from ‚ÄúJoker.‚Äù

Phillips, who was nominated for Oscars for directing, writing and producing ‚ÄúJoker,‚Äù directed ‚ÄúJoker: Folie √Ä Deux‚Äù from a screenplay by fellow Oscar nominee Scott Silver & Phillips, based on characters from DC.  The film was produced by Phillips, Oscar nominee Emma Tillinger Koskoff and Joseph Garner.  Lady Gaga served as music consultant.  The film‚Äôs executive producers are Michael E. Uslan, Georgia Kacandes, Silver, Mark Friedberg and Jason Ruder.

Working with Phillips behind the camera are his team from ‚ÄúJoker,‚Äù including Oscar-nominated director of photography Lawrence Sher, production designer Mark Friedberg, Oscar-nominated editor Jeff Groth, and composer Hildur Guƒënad√≥ttir, who won the Oscar for her work on the first film.  New to the team is Oscar-nominated costume designer Arianne Phillips (‚ÄúOnce Upon a Time in‚Ä¶ Hollywood,‚Äù ‚ÄúDon‚Äôt Worry Darling‚Äù).  Ruder is the film‚Äôs executive music producer and the music supervisors are Randall Poster and George Drakoulias.  Casting is by Francine Maisler (the ‚ÄúDune‚Äù films, ‚ÄúChallengers‚Äù).

Warner Bros. Pictures Presents A Joint Effort Production, A Film by Todd Phillips, ‚ÄúJoker: Folie √Ä Deux.‚Äù  The film will be released worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures, and will be only in theaters nationwide on October 4, 2024, and beginning internationally on 2 October, 2024.

About CID:
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

snippet.title: MAHARAJA Movie Reaction Part (1/3)! | Vijay Sethupathi | Anurag Kashyap | Mamta Mohandas
snippet.description:
Jaby and Steph react to 'Maharaja', an intense action thriller that keeps you on the edge of your seat. 'Maharaja' is a must-watch for its thrilling plot and powerful performances.

Starring the phenomenal Vijay Sethupathi (Master & Vikram), Anurag Kashyap (Gangs of Wasseypur & Sacred Games), and Mamta Mohandas (Forensic & Johny Johny Yes Appa), this film tells the gripping story of a barber turned avenger. Directed by Nithilan Swaminathan and supported by a stellar cast including Natarajan Subramaniam (Naadodigal & Vada Chennai) and Abhirami Gopikumar (Aramm & Kalavani).

snippet.title: North Indian Vs South Indian Food Eating Challenge üî•|| FoodieWe 24hrs Challenge
snippet.description:
North Indian Vs South Indian Food Eating Challenge || Foodiewe 24hrs Challenge
1000 Rupees Challenge 

Welcome to another exciting food challenge on FoodieWe! üéâ This time, we're diving deep into the vibrant flavors of South Indian and North Indian cuisines. Mukti has set a thrilling challenge for Onkar and Aditya: survive on just ‚Çπ1000 for an entire day! But there's a twist‚ÄîAditya must savor only South Indian delicacies, while Onkar enjoys the rich tastes of North Indian fare.


From crispy dosas and spicy sambars to buttery naans and flavorful curries, this video is packed with mouthwatering and tempting dishes that will leave you craving more. Watch as Onkar and Aditya navigate their budgets, explore the diverse culinary landscapes, and compete to see who can eat the most delicious food.

Warning: Do not watch this video if you're hungry‚Äîresisting these tantalizing treats will be nearly impossible! üçõüç≤

Join us on this culinary adventure and find out who will emerge victorious in the ultimate food challenge. Don't forget to like, comment, and subscribe to FoodieWe for more epic food battles and delicious content!

#FoodChallenge #FoodieWe

Location 

1) Preet ( Time Till 2pm )- phase 7 mohali
2) Sardaji Dahi Bhalli (Time 11 am)- 3b1 Mohali
3) Shardai - 3b2 Mohali ( opp market near park )
4) nagpal - sector 34 chandigarh 
5) brother kulcha - sector 9 chandigarh 
6) gol gappe & jalebi - sector 32 street vendors market

snippet.description:

Watch the full episodes of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSKo8X_EiY0WewaBlNt49g3

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada

Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide

Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi

Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey

Shiddat Episode 49 [Eng Sub] - Muneeb Butt - Anmol Baloch - 23rd July 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Asra, a beautiful and cherished young woman, has led a life filled with love and care from her family. In contrast, Sultan, a determined and charismatic perfectionist, overcomes the challenges of his troubled childhood to consistently achieve his desires.

Despite their stark personality differences, Asra falls in love with Sultan. However, after they marry, Asra realizes that Sultan is not the ideal man she had envisioned. To please him, she sacrifices her desires and undergoes a significant transformation.

This revelation becomes the catalyst for an unending series of problems between them. The journey through marital life becomes a complex maze as Asra and Sultan attempt to navigate challenges, each trying to mold the other according to their own will and preference.

Will Asra and Sultan change for each other, or will the growing list of problems between them persist? When Asra discovers the reality about Sultan, how will she react? Is Sultan contemplating leaving Asra? Can love overcome all obstacles, or are some differences too profound to bridge?

snippet.description:

Habil Aur Qabil 2nd Last Episode 45 - [Eng Sub] - Aagha Ali - Yashma Gill - Asad Siddiqui - Nawal Saeed - 25th July 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Haris, a young and handsome perfectionist, excels in every aspect of life, often overshadowing his younger brother Qadir, who is dull and simple. Despite Qadir's sacrifices for his brother's happiness, Haris always gets his way.

Meanwhile, Sobia, a clever but impoverished relative of Haris and Qadir, manipulates Qadir into falling in love with her, leading to their impending marriage. As Haris struggles with his romantic pursuits, facing obstacles with his love, Hooram, jealousy drives him to abandon Hooram and
pursue Sobia. This decision sparks tension between the brothers, exacerbated when Sobia exploits the situation to her advantage.

Will Haris end up with Sobia? Will Qadir stand up against his brother? Will Hooram discover the real reason why Haris left her? Will Sobia choose Haris over Qadir? Will Qadir forever live in Haris's shadow?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Director: Aabis Raza
Writer: Zanjabeel Asim

Cast:
Aagha Ali as Haris

Mahmood Aslam as Qasim

Zia Gurchani as Mahmood

snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Watch the full episodes of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSKo8X_EiY0WewaBlNt49g3

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku
